description: I am an honest, sincere, faithful and loyal woman, with good values, with love and respect for the family and others, I am cheerful and I like to make others laugh, I am outgoing, risky, daring and persevering.And determined, I am extremely passionate in every aspect of my life, affectionate, romantic and loving. I am looking for a life and adventure partner, an accomplice in my madness, a best friend and confidant,The love of my life, my soulmate, an honest, noble man with good feelings, who loves and respects himself as well as those around him, without fear of pursuing his dreams, but above all , without fear of living fully every moment of his life and being able to accept and love me as I am
